      <title>俄罗斯黑客瞄准 WhatsApp 寻求乌克兰数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/whatsapp-targeted-by-russian-hackers-seeking-info-on-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据微软公司称，一个与俄罗斯政府有关联的黑客组织试图窃取向乌克兰提供援助的非政府组织员工的 WhatsApp 数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/whatsapp-targeted-by-russian-hackers-seeking-info-on-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Anduril 的 Luckey 指出无人机产量竞争中存在中国风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/anduril-to-locate-5-million-square-foot-drone-factory-in-ohio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防科技初创公司 Anduril Industries Inc. 已选择俄亥俄州作为其大型新制造工厂的所在地，该工厂将每年生产数万套自主系统和武器，这是其成为美国军方无人机和其他技术主要供应商计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/anduril-to-locate-5-million-square-foot-drone-factory-in-ohio</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
